name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: May And Kyogre Pokemon Live Wallpaper

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Dive into an unforgettable Pokémon adventure with the May and Kyogre Pokémon Live Wallpaper.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome extension transforms your new tab into a mesmerizing ocean scene featuring May and the legendary Kyogre. Whether you're a long-time fan of Pokémon or love serene, aquatic themes, this wallpaper brings a touch of the Hoenn region to your browser.

Features:
🌊 A stunning live wallpaper featuring May and Kyogre in a breathtaking underwater setting.
🌐 Customizable search bar to access your preferred search engine.
🕒 Integrated clock and date display to keep you on schedule.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts for seamless navigation to your top websites.
Let the serene beauty of Kyogre's domain and May's adventurous spirit inspire your browsing experience every day.
